<div class="bg-white min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <!-- Breadcrumb & Back -->
    <%= link_to "← 목록으로 돌아가기", properties_path, class: "text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium mb-8 inline-block" %>

    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-12">
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <% @property.tags.each do |tag| %>
              <span class="bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-slate-600"><%= tag.icon %> <%= tag.name %></span>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4"><%= @property.title %></h1>
          <div class="flex items-center text-slate-500 font-medium">
            <span class="mr-2">📍</span><%= @property.location %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Gallery Placeholder -->
        <div class="aspect-video bg-slate-100 rounded-3xl mb-12 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400">
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="text-6xl mb-4 block">📸</span>
            <p class="font-medium">고화질 감성 사진 갤러리 영역</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Host Story Section -->
        <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">호스트 이야기</h2>
          <div class="bg-green-50/50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-green-100/50 mb-12">
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-wrap"><%= @property.description %></p>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">이곳에서의 경험</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none p-0">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
              <span class="text-xl">☕</span>
              <span class="text-slate-700 font-medium font-medium">핸드드립 커피 체험</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
              <span class="text-xl">🚜</span>
              <span class="text-slate-700 font-medium font-medium">계절 농사 체험</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-amber-500">⚠️</span> 정직한 불편함
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">ChonCance는 완벽함보다 진정성을 추구합니다. 아래 내용을 반드시 확인해주세요.</p>
            <div class="bg-amber-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-amber-100 text-amber-900 text-sm">
              <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-4">
                <li>시골 특성상 작은 벌레가 출몰할 수 있습니다.</li>
                <li>오래된 한옥이라 방음이 완벽하지 않을 수 있습니다.</li>
                <li>마을 버스 배차 간격이 기니 자차 이용을 권장합니다.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar: Booking Card -->
      <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <div class="sticky top-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl bg-white">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900"><%= number_with_delimiter(@property.price_per_night) %>원</span>
              <span class="text-slate-500"> / 1박</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-500 text-sm">
              <span>★</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-slate-900">4.9</span>
              <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">(후기 12개)</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-4 border-r border-slate-200">
                <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">체크인</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">날짜 선택</div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">체크아웃</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">날짜 선택</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl">
              <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase">인원</div>
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">게스트 2명</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%= link_to "예약 요청하기", "#", class: "w-full bg-green-700 text-white text-center block py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold shadow-lg hover:bg-green-800 transition transform active:scale-95" %>
          
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] text-center mt-4">예약 확정 전에는 결제가 진행되지 않습니다.</p>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-200 rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">슈퍼호스트 김영희님</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">응답률 100% · 24시간 내 응답</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
